data.description: MLS# 14530555 - Built by Highland Homes - Ready Now! ~ The entrance to this one-story home could easily be full of country charm with its big front porch.  The study is set back off the main entry hallway at the front of the house.  The three secondary bedrooms share a game room which is tucked away from the family room.  Open concept family, kitchen and breakfast are at the rear of the home overlooking the backyard.
